Motormaster gets out of Astroblast and stretches. "You arent in any shape
to fight Atroblast, and you know it" Motormaster mentions. He gets back
inside, and remerges, with Dead-End's smoking body over one shoulder, and
the pile of Beastbox in his other hand. He starts to move towards the base,
waiting for Astroblast to join him.
